metadata.description:
Wize Fellaz Bronze Edition is a collection of 5.000 NFTs depicting timeless OGs who have been fighting the forces of chaos since the beginning of time by harnessing the power of Spring Tea, a wondrous cocktail that prolongs life, grants supernatural powers, and drives users slightly kooky. Our collection capitalizes on the incredible power of original art and storytelling to build a vibrant Web3 brand.

Beyond financial growth and sustainability, our community seeks to support institutions that improve the lives of older adults suffering from poverty and social exclusion.

Join us on Twitter @wizefellaz and on the web https://www.wizefellaz.com
metadata.name: Wize Fellaz Bronze Edition #1
